Interface FlightRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface FlightRepository
extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<Flight,java.lang.Long>
    This interface extends JpaRepository and has methods to list distinct values from the entity and filter flight by codeFlight.
